      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "The old way: Hire more people to handle more work.\n\nThe better way: Streamline your processes so your current team handles more.\n\nOne approach scales your costs.\nThe other scales your capacity.\n\nMost businesses have 15-20 hours of work per week that could be automated or eliminated entirely.\n\nThe question isn't whether you can afford to improve efficiency.\nIt's whether you can afford not to.\n\nWhat process in your business feels more complicated than it should be?",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The old way: Hire more people to handle more work.\n\nThe better way: Streamline your processes so your current team handles more.\n\nOne approach scales your costs.\nThe other scales your capacity.\n\nMost businesses have 15-20 hours of work per week that could be automated or eliminated entirely.\n\nThe question isn't whether you can afford to improve efficiency.\nIt's whether you can afford not to.\n\nWhat process in your business feels more complicated than it should be?",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a7",
      "autoResize": true
    },
