      "updated": 1768931857587,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "I've noticed something about efficient businesses:\n\nThey don't work harder. They work cleaner.\n\nTheir processes flow instead of tangle.\nTheir data moves instead of sits.\nTheir team focuses instead of firefights.\n\nThe difference? They took time to untangle the knots.\n\nEvery business has them - those processes that \"work\" but waste everyone's time.\n\nThe transformation happens when you finally address them.\n\nWhat's one process you've been meaning to fix?",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "I've noticed something about efficient businesses:\n\nThey don't work harder. They work cleaner.\n\nTheir processes flow instead of tangle.\nTheir data moves instead of sits.\nTheir team focuses instead of firefights.\n\nThe difference? They took time to untangle the knots.\n\nEvery business has them - those processes that \"work\" but waste everyone's time.\n\nThe transformation happens when you finally address them.\n\nWhat's one process you've been meaning to fix?",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
